d class citizens\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2100}, {\"ngram\": \"their Olympic outfits\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, other athletes pointed out that female athletes will have a range of designs to choose from and may opt to wear the men's kits if they wish.\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2280, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other athletes\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"female athletes\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2187}, {\"ngram\": \"a range\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2205}, {\"ngram\": \"designs\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2216}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's kits\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic pole vaulter Katie Moon said: \\\"I absolutely love people defending women, but we have at least 20 different combinations of a uniform to compete in with all the tops and bottoms available to us.\\\"\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2309, \"end\": 2313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moon\", \"score\": 0.999999999738975, \"rank\": 2.0267982205176711e-10, \"text\": \"Moon\", \"types\": [\"Q634\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2345}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2361}, {\"ngram\": \"at least 20 different combinations\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2409}, {\"ngram\": \"a uniform\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2422}, {\"ngram\": \"all the tops\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2454}, {\"ngram\": \"bottoms\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2466}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports giant Nike defended the outfits saying, \\\"The goal was to offer options that met athletes' desires for choice, comfort and performance.\\\"\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2499, \"end\": 2503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.999850043128