ocus on their attire and body shapes rather than their abilities and performance.\", \"from\": 5146, \"to\": 5352, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Experts\", \"from\": 5146, \"to\": 5153}, {\"ngram\": \"another reason\", \"from\": 5158, \"to\": 5172}, {\"ngram\": \"so many women\", \"from\": 5173, \"to\": 5186}, {\"ngram\": \"professional sports\", \"from\": 5199, \"to\": 5218}, {\"ngram\": \"female athletes\", \"from\": 5227, \"to\": 5242}, {\"ngram\": \"their attire\", \"from\": 5279, \"to\": 5291}, {\"ngram\": \"body shapes\", \"from\": 5296, \"to\": 5307}, {\"ngram\": \"their abilities\", \"from\": 5320, \"to\": 5335}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 5340, \"to\": 5351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is unfortunate that far too often, attention is paid more on how women athletes look, versus their power, grit and performance,\\\" Danette Leighton, CEO of the New York-based nonprofit Women's Sports Foundation, told Al Jazeera in a written statement.\", \"from\": 5354, \"to\": 5607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5495, \"end\": 5503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederic_Leighton\", \"score\": 0.9999981264049255, \"rank\": 1.7726436796503376e-06, \"text\": \"Leighton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederic_Leighton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederic_Leighton\"}, {\"begin\": 5573, \"end\": 5583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 0.9999999367860275, \"rank\": 6.321384243512375e-08, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 5393, \"to\": 5402}, {\"ngram\": \"women athletes\", \"from\": 5423, \"to\": 5437}, {\"ngram\": \"their power\", \"from\": 5451, \"to\": 5462}, {\"ngram\": \"grit\", \"from\": 5464, \"to\": 5468}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 5473, \"to\": 5484}, {\"ngram\": \"CEO\", \"from\": 5505, \"to\": 5508}, {\"ngram\": \"the New York-based nonprofit Women's Sports Foundation\", \"from\": 5512, \"to\": 5566}, {\"ngram\": \"a written statement\", \"from\": 5587, \"to\": 5606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We believe clothing should help athletes feel empowered to do their best, not overshadow their efforts or bring undue scrutiny.\", \"from\": 5609, \"to\": 5737, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"clothing\", \"from\": 5621, \"to\": 5629}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 5642, \"to\": 5650}, {\"ngram\": \"their best, not overshadow their efforts\", \"from\": 5672, \"to\": 5712}, {\"ngram\": \"undue scrutiny\", \"from\": 5722, \"to\": 5736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is opportunity for sport governing bodies, sponsors, and all involved, to be more thoughtful and inclusive,\\\" Leighton said.\", \"from\": 5739, \"to\": 5869, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5855, \"end\": 5863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederic_Leighton\", \"score\": 0.9999981264049255, \"rank\": 1.7726436796503376e-06, \"text\": \"Leighton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederic_Leighton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederic_Leighton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"opportunity\", \"from\": 5749, \"to\": 5760}, {\"ngram\": \"sport governing bodies\", \"from\": 5765, \"to\": 5787}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsors\", \"from\": 5789, \"to\": 5797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Al Jazeera English:\", \"from\": 5889, \"to\": 5915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Al Jazeera English\", \"from\": 5889, \"to\": 5914}]}]}"